      "side": 1,
      "message": "Also, to prevent mistakes, I think we should enforce that the full `cue mod tidy` is happy before a `cue mod publish` actually publishes; that is, I should not be allowed to publish with a stale `module.cue` when `local-module.cue` has higher dependency versions that `tidy` would apply to `module.cue`.",
